                  >
                    <p>Unlike most other templates/themes, you don't have to buy a new Tailwind Plus license every time you want to use it on a new project.</p>
                    <p>As long as what you're building is allowed as per the license, you can build as many sites as you want without ever having to buy an additional license.</p>
