                  >
                    <p>Yes! As long what you're building is a custom website developed for a single client, you can totally use components and templates in Tailwind Plus to help build it.</p>
                    <p>The only thing you can't do is use Tailwind Plus to build a website or template that is resold to multiple clients.</p>
                    <p>For more information and examples, <a href="/plus/license">read through our license</a>.</p>
